OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1772637082
OL,3,CTrial begins of man accused of rape
OL,4,Cfor which man was wrongly convicted
OL,6,FMr Price said: "Andrew Malkinson was
OL,7,Fnot to be released from this sentence
OL,8,Funtil December 2020. Mr Malkinson
OL,9,Fserved more than seventeen years in
OL,10,Fprison."
OL,12,FThe trial continues.
OL,26,@nD@POU
